                  </hi>. I am shopman to Mr. Fairland, of Lisson-grove. I produce a gown pawned by a female—I believe the prisoner to be the person—this duplicate is what I gave her.</p>
               <p>(<hi rend="italic">Property produced and sworn to.</hi>)</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I am very sorry for it. I did it on purpose to get into prison again. I wished to retrieve my character. My father and mo<lb></lb>ther would not let me in. I had rather be transported.</p>
